    • equals

      public static boolean equals(NamedStack<CTStackItem> stack1, NamedStack<CTStackItem> stack2)

      Returns true if the two specified Stacks are equal to one another.

      Two Stacks are considered equal if they contain the same number of elements, and all corresponding pairs of elements in the two arrays are equal.

      Parameters:
      stack1 - one Stack to be tested for equality
      stack2 - the other Stack to be tested for equality
      Returns:
      true if the two Stacks are equal
